      "title": "The interim budget is passed with a majority of 115 votes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The interim budget presented by President Ranil Wickremesinghe as the Finance Minister was passed with a majority of 115 votes. It received 120 votes in favor and 5 votes against. 43 ministers abstained from voting."
